  "root_text": {
    "iti23:0.1": "Itivuttaka 23 ",
    "iti23:0.2": "Ekakanipāta ",
    "iti23:0.3": "Tatiyavagga ",
    "iti23:0.4": "Ubhayatthasutta ",
    "iti23:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti23:2.1": "“Ekadhammo, bhikkhave, bhāvito bahulīkato ubho atthe samadhigayha tiṭṭhati—",
    "iti23:2.2": "diṭṭhadhammikañceva atthaṁ samparāyikañca. ",
    "iti23:2.3": "Katamo ekadhammo? ",
    "iti23:2.4": "Appamādo kusalesu dhammesu. ",
    "iti23:2.5": "Ayaṁ kho, bhikkhave, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato ubho atthe samadhigayha tiṭṭhati—",
    "iti23:2.6": "diṭṭhadhammikañceva atthaṁ samparāyikañcā”ti. ",
    "iti23:2.7": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti23:2.8": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti23:3.1": "“Appamādaṁ pasaṁsanti, ",
    "iti23:3.2": "puññakiriyāsu paṇḍitā; ",
    "iti23:3.3": "Appamatto ubho atthe, ",
    "iti23:3.4": "adhigaṇhāti paṇḍito. ",
    "iti23:4.1": "Diṭṭhe dhamme ca yo attho, ",
    "iti23:4.2": "yo cattho samparāyiko; ",
    "iti23:4.3": "Atthābhisamayā dhīro, ",
    "iti23:4.4": "paṇḍitoti pavuccatī”ti. ",
    "iti23:5.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti23:5.2": "Tatiyaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti23:0.1": "So It Was Said 23 ",
    "iti23:0.2": "The Book of the Ones ",
    "iti23:0.3": "Chapter Three ",
    "iti23:0.4": "Both Kinds of Benefit ",
    "iti23:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti23:2.1": "“This one thing, mendicants, when developed and cultivated, secures equal benefits for both ",
    "iti23:2.2": "this life and lives to come. ",
    "iti23:2.3": "What one thing? ",
    "iti23:2.4": "Diligence in skillful qualities. ",
    "iti23:2.5": "This is the one thing that, when developed and cultivated, secures equal benefits for both ",
    "iti23:2.6": "this life and lives to come.” ",
    "iti23:2.7": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti23:2.8": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti23:3.1": "“The astute praise diligence ",
    "iti23:3.2": "in making merit. ",
    "iti23:3.3": "Being diligent, an astute person ",
    "iti23:3.4": "secures both benefits: ",
    "iti23:4.1": "the benefit in this life, ",
    "iti23:4.2": "and in lives to come. ",
    "iti23:4.3": "Attentive, comprehending the meaning, ",
    "iti23:4.4": "they are said to be astute.” ",
    "iti23:5.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
